channel.title: 474 Development Team
channel.description:
[center]Project no-name is an outstanding project in the process of being created by me, and others eventually soon. The base is [b]Hyperion 474[/b] and is being worked on hard to produce the maxium standards it should be, but we can only do this with your help. A development thread will be posted soon for the latest Development on the Server.[/center] [center][u][b]About the Server[/b][/u] This 474 is extremely unique, with most basic 474 features (none-combat skills) and with a fully functioning combat. The Economy is hard, and in my opinion it needs to be loosend a little, this will be worked upon. 474 Mapdata dumped (Thing1) Login Rendering [/center] [center]More information soon as I havn't much time.[/center] [u][b]Proof of Development;[/b][/u] [url=http://s1141.photobucket.com/albums/n584/Entinity/?action=view¤t=Clip.mp4]Fully initialized calculated timing hits via Skillcape Emotes.[/url] [url=http://s1141.photobucket.com/albums/n584/Entinity/?action=view¤t=NICE.mp4]Perfected Pking combinations.[/url] As you may or may not know, most of my Developments have been a failure, due to backstabbers and people that arn't active enough, well I can tell you now, this won't be a failure, and [b]I will[/b] pick the right team. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- If you wish to apply for Staff you [b]cannot[/b] apply or be in any other team then this. [u]The Team and positions[/u] [b]Server Developer(s); X Entinity X, Python_ [/b] [b]Forum Developer(s); Jordan Cardewell, Soul My Maul[/b] [b]Administrator(s); Mac, Mss Destiny[/b] [b]Moderator(s); -[/b] [b]Gfx Designer(s); -[/b] If you'd like to join this Development Team to create this Server, please fillout the format below.
How old are you? How long have you been coding Java? What revision do you code? What are you applying for? Why would you like to join? Do you have; Skype, MSN or Ventrilo? Do you play any other games? Any other additinal information can be posted here.
If you wish to contact me, entinity@hotmail.co.uk.
